videos.description: Bojan Bogdanovic confidently nails his 6th 3-pointer of the first quarter to pad the Jazz's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bogdanovic scorches Clippers with his 6th 3 in the first quarter) 2021/6/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bogdanovic scorches Clippers with his 6th 3 in the first quarter

videos.description: Luke Kennard doesn't have an answer for Jordan Clarkson's smooth side-step 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Clarkson nails nasty side-step 3-pointer on Kennard) 2021/6/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clarkson nails nasty side-step 3-pointer on Kennard

videos.description: Rudy Gobert takes issue with Marcus Morris Sr. stepping over him and grabs his leg. They both receive technical fouls for the incident.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert, Morris receive double T's for incident under basket) 2021/6/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert, Morris receive double T's for incident under basket

videos.description: Paul George weaves through the lane and avoids contact with Rudy Gobert for the basket.

videos.headline: PG-13 avoids Gobert midair for bucket

videos.description: Steve Ballmer can't contain his excitement after Marcus Morris Sr. drains the 3-pointer.

videos.description: Joe Ingles grabs the steal and dishes to Rudy Gobert who flies through the lane for a roaring slam.
